sorts Oid Uid Data Expr NonPrivData PrivData MsgId Vid .
subsort NonPrivData PrivData < Data .
subsort Oid MsgId Uid < NonPrivData .
subsort Data < Expr .
subsort Qid < Vid < Expr .
